Package model

Class Diagnosis

java.lang.Object
model.Diagnosis
public class Diagnosis extends Object
Represents a Diagnosis made for a patient, which includes details such as the diagnosis description, treatment plans, prescriptions, and relevant IDs for patient, doctor, and medical records.

      public Diagnosis(String patientID, String diagnosisID, String doctorID, String medicalRecordID, LocalDateTime diagnosisDate, Treatment Treatment, String diagnosisDescription, Prescription prescription)
      Constructs a Diagnosis object with the specified details.
      Parameters:
      patientID - the unique identifier for the patient
      diagnosisID - the unique identifier for the diagnosis
      doctorID - the unique identifier for the doctor who made the diagnosis
      medicalRecordID - the medical record ID associated with the diagnosis
      diagnosisDate - the date and time when the diagnosis was made
      Treatment - the treatment plans associated with the diagnosis
      diagnosisDescription - the description of the diagnosis
      prescription - the prescription given as part of the diagnosis
